features: 🍅 Kids Art Frames Set Size --- This child artwork frames is perfect for showcasing children's artwork, with a size of 10x12.5 inches without mat or 8.5x11 inches with mat. Its rustic style allows it to display different sizes of artwork, depending on whether a mat is used or not.

🍅 Art Storage Frame --- With a thickness of 0.78 inches, this high capacity storage picture frame can generally hold 50-150 pieces of paper, although this may vary depending on the thickness and material of the paper. It's a great way to display a variety of items, including children's artwork, photos, postcards, concert tickets, and more.

🍅 Easy to Hang --- 180° front-opening interchangeable frame, and can be hung in both horizontal and vertical orientations. It's secured with an elastic band and has a clear view glass. This flexibility makes it easy for children to change up their paintings drawings whenever they want, showcasing their creativity in new and exciting ways.

🌶 Wide Application --- This frame has a wide range of applications and can not only be used as a kid's art display frame for paintings, certificates, documents, photos, landscapes, and illustrations, but also as storage frames, allowing you to preserve other cherished memories, such as photographs.

🌶 Great Gift Idea --- This kids drawing art frame set makes for the perfect gift for birthdays, housewarming days, Christmas, and Thanksgiving Day. It shows your care and love for your kids, relatives, and friends while encouraging children to take pride in their artwork and display it confidently.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love The Frames
reviews.reviewText: I bought 3 each. One was broken. They sent me new. My granddaughters art and school work looks amazing in these frames! I recommend these to grandparents and mom and dads! I love them! They are made well and well worth the purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is the best kept secret available these days!
reviews.reviewText: This is the best value-for-the-money item I've purchased this year. The quality is top notch. The design is cleaver. They are amazingly easy to use. They are designed for kids artwork and I guess this is why they have kept the price so reasonable. I am using them for my living room design and am going to print or have printed my iphone pics of family and vacation and rotatate it. I'm also buying 2 for my niece to display her kid's artwork because using it as intended is an awesome idea. I love, love, love these frames.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I night similar products before but this one is better quality, price and very well packaged. Very happy with the purchase!

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Child art displays
reviews.reviewText: These are cute and appear to be well made. They weigh less than 2 pounds so I used command picture frame strips to hang them instead of screws in my wall. I use them to display my grandson's artwork.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Solves delimna of how to keep up and display the parade of child creations that comes home from school. You treasure and WANT to put them up and this gives them a worthy and lovely place to be displayed as well as save their works of art. Got one for each grandchild. Just perfect.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars PERFECT gift for a mom
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I have wanted these for so long and I LOVE them!! My kids are so excited to see their art displayed. They have hooks for hanging on the back but I hung with command strips and they are very well secured to the wall. Light weight and easy to hang. The hinges are sturdy and nothing about the frames looks or feels flimsy. It’s such a GREAT gift item! I’m buying for my mom friend for Christmas ❤️

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Received the first package to find one of the two frames were broken. Contacted Amazon and they replaced it immediately. I applied quite a few magnets on the back so it would adhere to my refrigerator. My grandkids are so happy their art work is displayed so beautifully.
